```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin UI
    participant API as Admin API
    participant Slots as Slots Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Public as Public API

    Admin->>API: GET /api/slots/{slot_id}
    API->>Slots: Загрузи конфигурацию + recent_results
    Slots->>DB: SELECT slot, recent job_history
    Slots-->>API: Данные слота + recent_results
    API-->>Admin: JSON (config, recent_results)
    loop Отображение
        Admin->>Public: GET /public/results/{job_id}
        Public-->>Admin: 200 (файл) или 410 (TTL истёк)
    end
```
